name: Conan O'Brian
monologue: President Obama spent last night in Las Vegas. This morning he woke up on his hotel room floor trying to figure out what to do about a tiger, baby and 9 percent unemployment.

name: Conan O'Brian
monologue: According to new polls that just came out, Mitt Romney does very well with Republican voters who make more than $200,000. Or as Romney calls them, “trailer trash.”

name: Conan O'Brian
monologue: A Florida man was recently arrested for taking up-skirt shots at Wal-Mart. It will come to trial as soon as they can find 12 jurors willing to look at up-skirt shots of Wal-Mart shoppers.

name: Jimmy Kimmel
monologue: Our show is 9 years old. If it lived in China, it would be making iPhones already.

name: Jimmy Kimmel
monologue: Nine years is like 40 Kim Kardashian marriages.

name: Jimmy Kimmel
monologue: There was another Republican debate in Florida tonight. What is left to know about these candidates? Is someone going to confess to a murder?

name: Jimmy Kimmel
monologue: Fortunately, tonight's debate was the last one we're going to see. The candidates are going to take a break, spending more time attacking the morals of their families.
